  "detailed_description": "If you want to slash and dash your way through enemies, fight difficult bosses, and collect unique items, then this 2D roguelike action game is for you. <br>Here’s what you get to do...<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/8570331ffb123e0e831f74080fe77e3e.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/8570331ffb123e0e831f74080fe77e3e.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/8570331ffb123e0e831f74080fe77e3e.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Use Different Fighting Skills To Help You Survive</u></strong></h2>Hack, slash, shoot, dodge, dash, and block using different fighting skills to beat your way through enemies and bosses. But it’s not all just mindless combat.  <br>You have to pay attention to different enemies and learn their patterns if you want to survive. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/5994bfb6f025e7c7695b1ee88b6756bf.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/5994bfb6f025e7c7695b1ee88b6756bf.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/5994bfb6f025e7c7695b1ee88b6756bf.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Collect Different Abilities On Every Run</u></strong></h2>Every run is different because you’ll never know what unique abilities you’ll pick up on your journey.  <br>And there are 760 unique abilities you can collect to help you survive your run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/81a66de4f910986dc0bb403292e2904f.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/81a66de4f910986dc0bb403292e2904f.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/81a66de4f910986dc0bb403292e2904f.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Choose A Companion That Compliments Your Playstyle</u></strong></h2>To help you fight your way through the Kingdom, there are 26 unique companions you can pick from.  <br>And because each companion is unique, you can pick one that matches your playstyle.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/83142d705c755e6fca62288823aa6ece.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/83142d705c755e6fca62288823aa6ece.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/83142d705c755e6fca62288823aa6ece.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>12 Different Levels</u></strong></h2>The levels are arranged in Battlezones. In each Battlezone you fight groups of Goo’s.  Once you clear the Goo’s, you fight a Boss.  Your reward? <br>You get to meet a merchant where you can buy loot to help you in the next Battlezone.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/91da886886995f952a5a0fe65bb79801.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/91da886886995f952a5a0fe65bb79801.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/91da886886995f952a5a0fe65bb79801.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>12 Unique And Difficult Boss Battles</u></strong></h2>Each boss you face will have their own unique patterns that you'll need to master. Different bosses will need different tactics.  <br>So part of your journey is to learn these bosses and adapt your skills to each one.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Thanks For Checking Out My Game!</u></strong></h2><br>Hey, my name is Velemir, here in Switzerland.  <br>I’m a solo game dev who made A Land Goo’s Crazy as a passion project.  I coded the game in Pixel Game Maker MV. Did the art myself.  And my bro helped with the amazing music and soundtrack.  <br><br>Anyway, thanks so much for checking out my game!  I hope you have fun playing the game and trying to figure out the dark lore and mystery behind the game.<br><br>- Velemir",
  "about_the_game": "If you want to slash and dash your way through enemies, fight difficult bosses, and collect unique items, then this 2D roguelike action game is for you. <br>Here’s what you get to do...<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/8570331ffb123e0e831f74080fe77e3e.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/8570331ffb123e0e831f74080fe77e3e.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/8570331ffb123e0e831f74080fe77e3e.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Use Different Fighting Skills To Help You Survive</u></strong></h2>Hack, slash, shoot, dodge, dash, and block using different fighting skills to beat your way through enemies and bosses. But it’s not all just mindless combat.  <br>You have to pay attention to different enemies and learn their patterns if you want to survive. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/5994bfb6f025e7c7695b1ee88b6756bf.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/5994bfb6f025e7c7695b1ee88b6756bf.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/5994bfb6f025e7c7695b1ee88b6756bf.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Collect Different Abilities On Every Run</u></strong></h2>Every run is different because you’ll never know what unique abilities you’ll pick up on your journey.  <br>And there are 760 unique abilities you can collect to help you survive your run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/81a66de4f910986dc0bb403292e2904f.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/81a66de4f910986dc0bb403292e2904f.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/81a66de4f910986dc0bb403292e2904f.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Choose A Companion That Compliments Your Playstyle</u></strong></h2>To help you fight your way through the Kingdom, there are 26 unique companions you can pick from.  <br>And because each companion is unique, you can pick one that matches your playstyle.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinli