.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Thanks For Checking Out My Game!</u></strong></h2><br>Hey, my name is Velemir, here in Switzerland.  <br>I’m a solo game dev who made A Land Goo’s Crazy as a passion project.  I coded the game in Pixel Game Maker MV. Did the art myself.  And my bro helped with the amazing music and soundtrack.  <br><br>Anyway, thanks so much for checking out my game!  I hope you have fun playing the game and trying to figure out the dark lore and mystery behind the game.<br><br>- Velemir",
